<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٣٥٨٨ - غ ف ر]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>غفَرَ١ يغفِر، غَفْرًا، فهو غَفِير، والمفعول مَغْفور<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• غفَر الشّيءَ:</span> ستره، خبَّأه.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>